title: Dakine Pyro Kite Harness
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2013 Pyro Kite Harness in Spark.
Pyro Kite Harness Features:
- Power Clip Lock buckle system
- Hammerhead spreader bar
- Ergonomic spreader bar pad
- Dual blade hook knife
- Pre-curved P.E.B. inner support structure
- Featherweight ES foam molded interior
- Spreader bar hold down webbing strap
- Two side key/knife pockets with elastic loop
- Independent primary and secondary power belt
- ntegrated handle and leash attachment
- Sliding Spreader Bar compatible
- Leverlock Spreader Bar compatible
